Package: distiller-migrator
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${python3:Depends},
         python3,
         apt
Description: Migration tool for Distiller platform package transitions
 This package provides tools and scripts to migrate the Distiller platform
 from the legacy pamir-ai package organization to the new pamir-ai-pkgs
 organization.
 .
 The migrator handles:
  * Repository configuration updates
  * Package deprecation and replacement
  * Smooth transition between package organizations
  * Rollback capabilities for failed migrations
 .
 This tool is essential for maintaining system consistency during platform
 updates and organizational changes.
